{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Argentina \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ee1 \u00f2a c\u1ea3m x\u00fac sau khi Marcos Rojo ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nigeria \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm qu\u00ean \u0111i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, \u0110T Argentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria. Messi sau m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho &lsquo;nh\u1eefng v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Tango&rsquo; ch\u1ec9 15 ph\u00fat sau khi b\u00f3ng l\u0103n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Argentina l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ch\u00f9ng xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 51. Trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i&nbsp;ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Argentina \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00e0n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau c\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Rojo trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2-1 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung l\u1edbn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecm l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i cho b\u00e0i to\u00e1n &ldquo;c\u00f4ng c\u00f9n, th\u1ee7 k\u00e9m&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1, 3-4-3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland v\u00e0 Croatia, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 4-4-2 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Lionel Mess - Gonzalo Higuian trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nigeria. Trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00f4 cao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Messi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngay trong hi\u1ec7p 1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc l\u00f3e s\u00e1ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a M10 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Argentina \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 theo k\u00e8m c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nigeria v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina 2-1 Nigeria Vui th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Argentina 2-1 Nigeria Vui th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/073419-5.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ngo\u00e0i b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, Messi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong tr\u1eadn&nbsp;</em><i>Argentina 2-1 Nigeria</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi b\u1ecb phong t\u1ecfa, Higuain c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n. M\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Juventus m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0110T Nigeria, tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Nigeria, Higuain l\u1ea1i s\u00fat b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 trong s\u1ef1 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Argentina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1edf, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 Argentina c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u00f4ng Cuneyt Cakir kh\u1eaft khe \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Argentina \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty. V\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 La Albiceleste l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Nigeria g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Javier Mascherano k\u00e9o ng\u00e3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1m n\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 non n\u1edbt v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 34 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Mascherano. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4n ngoan h\u01a1n, ng\u00f4i sao t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i Argentina v\u1eabn b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi g\u1eb7p d\u00e0n sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1ed1n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/Ket-qua-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-tran-dau-bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nigeria 1-2 Argentina (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p sau 90 ph\u00fat ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf. Messi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng Moses g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Argentina may m\u1eafn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia nh\u01b0 Willy Caballero, Aguero, Salvio, Acuna,&hellip; \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Franco Armani, Marcos Rojo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Ever Banega, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nigeria.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i vi\u1ec7c tung Banega v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Argentina thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Sevilla c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn khi tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tinh t\u1ebf cho Messi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. Nh\u1edd ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o c\u00f9ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u1ed1t, Banega \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Argentina l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nhau th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t kh\u1ed1i th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t, \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 La Albiceleste v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch mang t\u00ean Nigeria t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ever Banega co mot tran dau an tuong\" title=\"Ever Banega c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/banega.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ever Banega c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Ever Banega l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 x\u00f4ng x\u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u00e0i hoa th\u00ec th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb Armani&nbsp;l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung c\u1ee7a Argentina. Trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh Argentina thay cho Caballero, Armani \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee9u thua cho Argentina. Ri\u00eang \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a Nigeria, Armani c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay, Marcos Rojo&nbsp;c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb pha b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p hai, Rojo tr\u1ea3i qua ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 74%, 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c v\u00e0 8 l\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Rojo ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf ph\u00fat 86.&nbsp;Rojo trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nigeria, \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho Argentina. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i n\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. Rojo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ee9 gi\u1eef v\u1eefng tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc &lsquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh Nigeria&rsquo;, tin r\u1eb1ng Argentina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-argentina-nghi-sao-ve-man-vuot-cua-tu-kich-tinh-421-189694.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/hlv-argentina-nghi-sao-ve-man-vuot-cua-tu-kich-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-argentina-nghi-sao-ve-man-vuot-cua-tu-kich-tinh-421-189694.html\">HLV Argentina ngh\u0129 sao v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1eeda t\u1eed k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina-421-189693.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina-421-189693.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina</span><br>\r\nArgentina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria-421-189686.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria-421-189686.html\">Messi n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria t\u1ed1i 26/6, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Messi cho bi\u1ebft anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;&#10;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"623","checkdouble":"189701"},{"date":"08:25 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 17h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-slna-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-276-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>SLNA vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (V\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 17h00 ng\u00e0y 276 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 17h00 ng\u00e0y 276 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/truc-tiep-sai-gon-vs-slna-162911.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">SLNA vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>SLNA vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: 1-0</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t SLNA thua tr\u1eadn \u1edf V-League 2018 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m 9/6 v\u1eeba qua. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng Lam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 leo l\u00ean th\u1ee9 10 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 17 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u01a1n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb san b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o, b\u1edfi l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi tranh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 chi\u1ec1u nay v\u00ec th\u1ebf mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng, SLNA s\u1ebd th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i h\u01a1n, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng l\u00fan s\u00e2u v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1. V\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u1edf V.League 2018, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ed5 sung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1eeba gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ecbnh Quang Vinh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u00ea Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f9ng B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n7 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n thua 4. H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 15 b\u00e0n l\u1ea7n, trong khi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn chu\u1ed7i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n khi \u0111\u00e1 xa nh\u00e0. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t S\u00f4ng Lam Ngh\u1ec7 An \u0111ang th\u0103ng hoa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nSLNA: V\u0169 H\u1ea3i, Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u00ecnh Ho\u00e0ng, V\u0103n Kh\u00e1nh, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, S\u1ef9 S\u00e2m, Ng\u1ecdc To\u00e0n, Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng, Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n, Tu\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Olaha.<br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n: \u0110\u1ee9c An, V\u0103n Ng\u1ecd, Ho\u00e0ng Qu\u1ea3ng, Th\u00e0nh T\u00edn, Anh V\u0169, Ng\u1ecdc Duy, Ho\u00e0ng Thi\u00ean, V\u0103n Tri\u1ec1n, Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, Xu\u00e2n D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Da Sylva.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"622","checkdouble":"189702"},{"date":"08:36 27/06","title":"V\u00ec sao tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cakir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed5i 11m cho Nigeria d\u00f9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/vi-sao-trong-tai-cakir-khong-thoi-11m-cho-nigeria-du-ap-dung-var.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 Cuneyt Cakir d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c khi kh\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed v\u1edbi Argentina \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video data-dashjs-player=\"\" src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/201806/273867/stream.mpd\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh anh h\u00f9ng c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i Argentina, trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m sau n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ighalo c\u1ee7a Nigeria.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nigeria, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cakir quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ra ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh. D\u1eabu v\u00e2y, sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi h\u01b0\u1edfng 11 m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPha quay ch\u1eadm \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fac Marcos Rojo nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi n\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eadp v\u00e0o tay. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cakir.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed5i 11m Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed5i 11m Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/roj.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rojo kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t 11 m sau pha \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo lu\u1eadt b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a FIFA, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ph\u1ea3i xem x\u00e9t nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n tay v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng (kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda b\u00e0n tay). \u1ede tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Rojo, tay c\u1ee7a anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp theo nh\u01b0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng. M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh ta c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh d\u00f9ng tay x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng h\u00f2ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay n\u00e0o trong khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh hay v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i xem x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u01b0\u1edfng 11 m hay kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-nhoc-nhan-vuot-ai-nigeria-vui-the-la-du-roi-421-189701.html\">Argentina nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Nigeria: Vui th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/toan-canh-man-thoat-chet-ngoan-muc-cua-argentina-421-189696.html\">To\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh m\u00e0n tho\u00e1t ch\u1ebft ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-argentina-nghi-sao-ve-man-vuot-cua-tu-kich-tinh-421-189694.html\">HLV Argentina ngh\u0129 sao v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1eeda t\u1eed k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina-421-189693.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-dua-argentina-vuot-qua-cua-tu-luon-la-mot-ngoi-sao-sang-choi-hon-tat-ca-421-189690.html\">Messi \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed: Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-truong-nigeria-argentina-di-tiep-nho-trong-tai-421-189689.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nigeria: Argentina \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria-421-189686.html\">Messi n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"621","checkdouble":"189703"},{"date":"08:53 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c (21h ng\u00e0y 27/6): Xe t\u0103ng v\u00e0o gu\u1ed3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-han-quoc-vs-duc-21h-ngay-276-xe-tang-vao-guong.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng khi m\u1edbi ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, Die Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ngay ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t Mexico \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i tranh c\u00e3i. V\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c (21h ng\u00e0y 276) Xe t\u0103ng v\u00e0o gu\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c (21h ng\u00e0y 276) Xe t\u0103ng v\u00e0o gu\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Nhan-dinh-Han-Quoc-vs-Duc-(21h-ngay-276)-Xe-tang-vao-guong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1eabn m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c, v\u1eabn m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng khoan nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, \u0110\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Joachim Loew d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng 2-1 nh\u1edd pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos d\u00f9 trong th\u1ebf ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Kroos \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft trong tay. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Die Mannschaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 d\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng khi m\u00e0 Mexico \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao (g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chat thep de Duc hoi sinh\" title=\"Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i sinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Chat-thep-de-Duc-hoi-sinh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00e1 r\u1ed9ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Loew th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1eafng. H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n mong manh v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 hai c\u00e1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat nh\u01b0 Thomas Muller, Timo Werner hay Mario Gomez \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec1u im ti\u1ebfng. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Marco Reus, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 Kroos v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/werner-phat-bieu-ve-dt-duc-va-viec-ghi-ban-421-189546.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/werner-phat-bieu-ve-dt-duc-va-viec-ghi-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/werner-phat-bieu-ve-dt-duc-va-viec-ghi-ban-421-189546.html\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do n\u00e0y, trung phong \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0ng chuy\u1ec7n ghi b\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n<span>Timo Werner ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ghi...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 sao, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i sinh. Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Trong 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c tin l\u00e0 th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u1edf m\u1ecdi tuy\u1ebfn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ng\u00e0y g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t, ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/son-heungmin-khoc-nuc-no-hua-giup-han-quoc-loai-duc-421-189440.html\" target=\"_blank\">Son Heung-min h\u1ee9a gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c lo\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c</span>. Nh\u01b0ng ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1ea5n an tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Han Quoc vs Mexico\" title=\"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/223052-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ef1c d\u1eady s\u0129 kh\u00ed H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nao nao. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 khi c\u1ea7n s\u1ebd \u0111em ra ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee9 b\u1eadc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, HLV Loew c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1eafm tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cam go ti\u1ebfp theo. Nh\u1eefng Werner, Mueller hay Gomez c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa h\u00edch t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kazan Arena t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 4 n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m vui r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra h\u01a1n c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nH\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (4-2-3-1):</strong> 23.Hyun-Woo - 2.Yong, 20.Hyun-Soo, 19.Young-Gwon, 12.Min-Woo - 16.Sung-yueng, 8.Se-Jong - 18.Seon-Min, 17.Jae-Sung, 11.Hee-Chan - 7.Heung-Min.<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ee9c (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Neuer - 18.Kimmich, 5.Hummels, 16.R\u00fcdiger, 3.Hector - 21.Gundogan, 8.Kroos - 13.Muller, 11.Reus, 9.Werner - 23.Gomez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: </strong>\u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eafng 3-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Han Quoc vs Duc\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Han-Quoc-vs-Duc-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-tro-joachim-low-nguoc-dong-ha-thuy-dien-vi-nguoi-duc-luon-thang-421-189536.html\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Low ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng h\u1ea1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: V\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c lu\u00f4n th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/su-co-hy-huu-sao-tuyen-duc-bi-thay-ra-vi-het-ao-mac-421-189479.html\">S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 hy h\u1eefu: Sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb thay ra v\u00ec\u2026 h\u1ebft \u00e1o m\u1eb7c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-ochoa-len-tieng-truoc-chien-thang-cua-duc-truoc-thuy-dien-421-189424.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ochoa l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-duc-21-thuy-dien-421-189417.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-nguoc-dong-kinh-di-ngay-ve-cua-marco-reus-421-189411.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh d\u1ecb: Ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Marco Reus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"620","checkdouble":"189704"},{"date":"08:53 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Brazil (1h ng\u00e0y 28/6): Nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa th\u00f4i c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-serbia-vs-brazil-1h-ngay-286-nhay-mua-thoi-cac-vu-cong.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Brazil ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Brazil l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd \u1edf th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, Brazil thu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c, T\u00e2y Ban Nha hay Argentina, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p. Ngay ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, h\u1ecd b\u1ecb Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi Costa Rica, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00f3t tim. Tr\u00f4i qua 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, Selecao v\u1eabn b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n 0-0. Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Philippe Coutinho m\u1edbi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Neymar \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 ch\u1ec9 6 ph\u00fat sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Brazil (1h ng\u00e0y 286) Nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa th\u00f4i v\u0169 c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Brazil (1h ng\u00e0y 286) Nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa th\u00f4i v\u0169 c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Nhan-dinh-Serbia-vs-Brazil-(1h-ngay-286)-Nhay-mua-thoi-vu-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc Costa Rica nh\u1edd 2 b\u00e0n ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh cho HLV Tite. \u00d4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi Douglas Costa hay Roberto Firmino c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 57 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, Brazil c\u00f3 b\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc ngay ph\u00fat 20. Nh\u01b0ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Tite xua qu\u00e2n v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1 cao s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, Zuber \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-20-costa-rica-khi-qua-khu-24-nam-ua-ve-421-189300.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/Philippe-Coutinho-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Brazil-vs-Costa-Rica-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-20-costa-rica-khi-qua-khu-24-nam-ua-ve-421-189300.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica: Khi qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 24 n\u0103m \u00f9a v\u1ec1\u2026</span><br>\r\n<span>T\u1ea1i World Cup 1994, Brazil ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. 24 n\u0103m sau, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite \u0111ang h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi Costa Rica, nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i v\u1edf t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u. Trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9 y nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Serbia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3 thi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra v\u1ec1 Brazil v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Tite \u0111ang b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ngay t\u1eeb khi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Tite kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 bung s\u1ee9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Ngay t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. M\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 d\u1eabn 1-0, Brazil c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eeba duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n, v\u1eeba kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite tinh toan sai lam\" title=\"HLV Tite tinh toan sai lam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/HLV-Tite-tinh-toan-sai-lam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Tite t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i cho Brazil</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i hay th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng qua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Serbia. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00f4i, Selecao v\u1eabn nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Brazil c\u0169ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, Serbia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb s\u1edbm. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng Dusko Tosic, Branislav Ivanovic r\u1ed3i Aleksandar Kolarov c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh l\u00e0 33 v\u00e0 t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. B\u00e0n thua quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Serbia c\u0169ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri b\u1ee9t \u0111i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n gi\u00f3, h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 34 tu\u1ed5i, Vladimir Stojkovic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Serbia vs Brazil\" title=\"Preview Serbia vs Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Serbia-vs-Brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Serbia vs Brazil 1h ng\u00e0y 28/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi, nh\u1eefng Neymar, Coutinho hay Gabriel Jesus h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd \u201ch\u00e0nh h\u1ea1\u201d c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Serbia c\u00f2n h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Brazil \u1edf th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Serbia 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a l\u00e0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Serbia, vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Brazil ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea1ng v\u1eeba v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d c\u00f3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n hay kh\u00f4ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0 nua c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00ec c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u201cv\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba\u201d tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. Ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u then ch\u1ed1t song k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nSerbia (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Stojkovic - 6.Ivanovic, 15.Milenkovic, 3.Tosic, 11.Kolarov - 4.Milivojevic, 21.Matic - 10.Tadic, 20.Milinkovic-Savic, 22.Ljajic - 9.Mitrovic<br>\r\n<strong>Brazil (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Alisson - 22.Fagner, 2.Silva, 3.Miranda, 12.Marcelo - 15.Paulinho, 5.Casemiro, 11.Coutinho - 19.Willian, 9.Jesus, 10.Neymar<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: </strong>Brazil th\u1eafng 2-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Serbia vs Brazil\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Serbia vs Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Serbia-vs-Brazil-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Serbia vs Brazil</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/he-lo-su-that-dang-sau-doi-tat-rach-cua-neymar-421-189441.html\">H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb1ng sau \u0111\u00f4i t\u1ea5t r\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lugano-khen-ngoi-neymar-va-tin-tuong-dt-brazil-421-189408.html\">V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Brazil v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesus-phat-bieu-ve-neymar-mit-uot-cua-dt-brazil-421-189354.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Brazil thanh minh cho th\u00f3i \u201cm\u00edt \u01b0\u1edbt\u201d c\u1ee7a Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-thuy-sy-phan-khich-sau-khi-cam-hoa-brazil-va-danh-bai-serbia-421-189343.html\">HLV Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch sau khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Brazil v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-thang-tran-world-cup-dau-tien-le-tru-ta-bat-dau-421-189322.html\">Brazil th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean: L\u1ec5 tr\u1eeb t\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u\u2026</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"619","checkdouble":"189705"},{"date":"04:02 27/06","title":"Ph\u00e1p th\u00e0 nh\u1ea1t nh\u1ebdo c\u00f2n h\u01a1n h\u00fat ch\u1ebft nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c hay TBN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/phap-tha-nhat-nheo-con-hon-hut-chet-nhu-duc-hay-tbn.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Didier Deschamps l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng thanh minh cho m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a thi\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f3 ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn lao \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/phap-tha-nhat-nheo-con-hon-hut-chet-nhu-duc-hay-tbn.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia v\u00e0 Peru gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i b\u1edfi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t nh\u1ebdo 0-0 v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, khi\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. D\u1eaft tay nhau \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, la \u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt t\u1eeb tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-dan-mach-vs-phap-463-189638.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p</span> l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng thanh minh cho th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cQuan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a n\u00ean m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cN\u00f3 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n c\u00e1c anh ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5y. H\u00e3y nh\u00ecn \u0110\u1ee9c hay T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng xem v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng h\u00fat ch\u1ebft trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u1edfi m\u1edf h\u01a1n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out. H\u00f4m nay m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 (21h00 ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 b\u1ea3y 30/6) s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn si\u00eau \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina. Lionel Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap-461-189661.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-dan-mach-vs-phap-421-189643.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-dan-mach-vs-phap-421-189643.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, clip b\u00e0n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"618","checkdouble":"189681"},{"date":"04:06 27/06","title":"HLV \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/doi-thu-tai-world-cup-2018-xem-thuong-tuyen-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018, \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a th\u00ec hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u1eaft tay nhau \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra theo \u0111\u00fang k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n m\u00e0 ph\u00eda \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huan luyen vien Age Hareide danh gia thap doi tuyen Phap o World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Age Hareide \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/doi-thu-tai-world-cup-2018-xem-thuong-tuyen-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV \u0110an M\u1ea1ch&nbsp;Age Hareide b\u00e1c b\u1ecf chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a nhau. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong khi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 v\u1eeba nghe ng\u00f3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa Peru v\u00e0 \u00dac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 0-0 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ebb nh\u1ea1t v\u00e0 k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u00f4ng Age Hareide cho hay: &ldquo;Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 ngu ng\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u1ea7n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. &ldquo;\u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m \u1edf m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cu\u1ed1i c\u0169ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Croatia, HLV Hareide n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Croatia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 1/7 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha/Nga \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Sochi v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/7.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap-461-189661.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap-461-189661.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia, hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u00f2a nh\u00e3, nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n \u0111\u1ebfn bu\u1ed3n ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-dan-mach-vs-phap-463-189638.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-dan-mach-vs-phap-463-189638.html\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p (KT): Les Bleus dung d\u0103ng dung d\u1ebb d\u1eaft l\u00ednh ch\u00ec v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia, hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u00f2a nh\u00e3, nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n \u0111\u1ebfn bu\u1ed3n ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-dan-mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien-khong-phai-anh-421-189245.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/christian-eriksen-dan-mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien-khong-phai-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-dan-mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien-khong-phai-anh-421-189245.html\">Christian Eriksen: \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i anh!</span><br>\r\nLi\u1ec7t k\u00ea th\u1eed xem nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay n\u00e0o! Argentina c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"617","checkdouble":"189682"},{"date":"03:49 27/06","title":"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/thong-ke-gay-soc-tran-nigeria-12-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria t\u1ed1i 26/6, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Messi cho bi\u1ebft anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018, \u0110T Argentina \u0111ang t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nigeria.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"messi argentina\" title=\"messi argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Messi ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Argentina c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi d\u00f9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y, M10 \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb TyC Sports: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Argentina s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Ch\u00faa tr\u1eddi lu\u00f4n b\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Ng\u00e0i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Argentina. T\u00f4i xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T Argentina v\u00ec s\u1ef1 hy sinh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng C\u0110V lu\u00f4n d\u00f5i theo v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Rojo&nbsp;&ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u1ea1i chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;B\u00e2y gi\u1edd th\u00ec World Cup m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Messi \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y t\u00f4i xin d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i v\u00e0 cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1ed1 l\u00ean Argentina!&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y 30/6 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf g\u1eb7p Uruguay/B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/Ket-qua-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-tran-dau-bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nigeria 1-2 Argentina (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p sau 90 ph\u00fat ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf. Messi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng Moses g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Argentina may m\u1eafn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-nigeria-463-189665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-nigeria-463-189665.html\">Nigeria 1-2 Argentina (KT): C\u1ee9u tinh Rojo \u0111\u01b0a Albiceleste v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ef1c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p sau 90 ph\u00fat ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf. Messi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng Moses g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Argentina may m\u1eafn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"616","checkdouble":"189683"},{"date":"04:14 27/06","title":"B\u1ecb Argentina lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng HLV Nigeria n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/bi-argentina-loai-day-cay-dang-hlv-nigeria-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nigeria b\u1ecb Argentina lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra, duy nh\u1ea5t Croatia l\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nigeria \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u1ecd t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i so v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/HLV-Gernot-Rohr-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria thua Argentina 1-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, Nigeria s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00fang gi\u00fap h\u1ecd r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang v\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft b\u1ea3ng D, Argentina v\u00e0 Nigeria \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. Messi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean, song s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u1edf ph\u00fat 51.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp Argentina bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed5ng l\u1ef1c. Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t tho\u00e1ng m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 86, Marcos Rojo d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-argentina-vs-nigeria-421-189676.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nigeria vs Argentina</span> c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 c\u1ee7a Iceland tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia gi\u00fap Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng Croatia b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f2n Argentina x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2. Nigeria v\u00e0 Iceland l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Gernot Rohr \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gernot Rohr phat bieu ve tran Nigeria vs Argentina\" title=\"Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/bi-argentina-loai-day-cay-dang-hlv-nigeria-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNigeria \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m, song ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c4 n\u0103m sau l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Nigeria \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"615","checkdouble":"189684"},{"date":"04:34 27/06","title":"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1eadn Iceland 1-2 Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/thong-ke-an-tuong-tran-iceland-12-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Iceland \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2, c\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3 - </strong>Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Croatia \u1edf World Cup, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Davor Suker (6) ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia - B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia - B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Thong-ke-Iceland-vs-Croatia---Bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 cho Croatia \u1edf World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>17 \u2013</strong> \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn 17 qu\u1ea3 11m, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf World Cup 1998.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>2 \u2013</strong> Croatia ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iceland v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-iceland-421-189675.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Iceland vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca r\u00f4 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>3 \u2013</strong> Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca r\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>100% -</strong> 80 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 79 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 100%.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>2 - </strong>Sigurdsson tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u00e3 1 l\u1ea7n ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 1 l\u1ea7n s\u00fat h\u1ecfng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf World Cup 2018, sau Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia - B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia - B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Thong-ke-Iceland-vs-Croatia---Bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sigurdsson g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Iceland tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2 \u2013</strong> \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Milan Badelj cho \u0110T Croatia, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean anh ghi v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Malta \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Euro 2012 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 2011.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>10 \u2013</strong> 10/11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong hi\u1ec7p 2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"614","checkdouble":"189685"}]}